Class Order

java.lang.Object
spss.project.backend.order.Order
public class Order extends Object
A class representing an order from a student to print a document.

      public Order(String studentId, String printerId, String documentId, String paperSize, List<Integer> pageNumbers, int numberOfCopies, boolean singleSided, LocalDateTime timeOrdered, boolean done)
      Creates a new order.
      Parameters:
      studentId - the ID of the student who submitted the order
      printerId - the ID of the printer on which the document was printed
      documentId - the ID of the document which was printed
      paperSize - the size of the paper which the document was printed on
      pageNumbers - the page numbers of the document which were printed
      numberOfCopies - the number of copies of the document which were printed
      singleSided - whether the document was printed single or double sided
      timeOrdered - the time at which the order was submitted
      done - whether the order was completed successfully
